Constantly find my hands in tightness/stiff/pain throughout the entire day..and I wake up in the middle of the night with my hands balled up in a fast. I try to take time breathing and they just never loosen up it seems..Been bothering me, so I had to art about it.
Daily digital abstract art using photoshop paint.
